{"tid":530751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五個月三死　酒店或低調做法事","createTime":"2018-01-16T05:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T07:35:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7cabebd4a098abd8dec4ef8c96971f21bd4506","tid":530751,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180116/20275634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F20275634&d=oJc%2BoIJJC6h83Z5gWO3x3P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=09d83b70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F20275634&h=be990b99\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180116/20275634</a><br />\n<br />\n五個月三死　酒店或低調做法事<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180116/large/16ls2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180116%2Flarge%2F16ls2p2.jpg&h=2943c407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麗思卡爾頓酒店5個月內發生兩宗命案。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前日發生南韓人殺妻兒兇案的香港麗思卡爾頓酒店，去年8月亦發生墮樓命案，酒店業人士指5個月內發生兩宗命案釀成3人死亡，相信對該酒店員工構成心理陰影，但酒店會否做法事超渡亡魂，視乎酒店管理公司及業主意願，但大原則是法事要低調進行，以免影響其他住客及酒店形象。<br />\n<br />\n他補充，酒店一般會在警方完成調查後即時更換肇事房間所有床單和被褥，並徹底清潔消毒。而法事一般是在短期內進行，大前提是盡量減低對其他住客的影響，可能會選在早上時間，或較少住客入住的日子，至於會否大陣仗封閉樓層則視乎需要，他指法事會令員工感到心安。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱指，平日酒店亦可能發生住客在房間或泳池猝死事故，一般酒店不會舉辦法事，但若家屬提出拜祭要求，酒店亦會酌情批准。<br />\n<br />\n■記者關英傑<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t涉殺妻兒韓CEO稱「斷片」指忘記曾致電友人求助<br />\n港聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"ef2c886ae24474787e35615bded42a5dc4d1c074","tid":530751,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:00:06.000Z","msg":"Ritz跳樓性地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c050f6024001efcd782343952cb6b85c4a2449d","tid":530751,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  爆房都唔敢去呢間"},{"pid":"430a99883177f209da0e700c8b8578480c9a6c07","tid":530751,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c050f6024001efcd782343952cb6b85c4a2449d","tid":530751,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  爆房都唔敢去呢間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:01:24.000Z","msg":"去奧運站上蓋果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5adadd85c9eaa95ebfbe950336c764a69dda1ea9","tid":530751,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:01:44.000Z","msg":"一析益下香港人住返幾晚撑旺個人氣咪無事囉"},{"pid":"70218777af7c0c41f65fbe84456d8e96b1ee35b1","tid":530751,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"RC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無大減價"},{"pid":"cf9a66601f2e7f5c31f180b3bdc467dfaebc5caa","tid":530751,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"國土鍊成陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33179c051947a963b0862f3050612de5e4fa153d","tid":530751,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"和尚fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dd0824b717fe847f4e9f3ce68d8def533dad0d","tid":530751,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c050f6024001efcd782343952cb6b85c4a2449d","tid":530751,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  爆房都唔敢去呢間"},"citedBy":0,"re